{"tid":1872617,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"武漢肺炎肆虐 熊本縣當局宣布熊本熊暫停與遊客直接接觸！","createTime":"2020-02-10T07:29:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-10T07:58:05.000Z","uid":63113,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d784d76285690da52c3cc4eb396f22e1630b0495","tid":1872617,"uid":63113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T07:29:08.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕中國武漢爆發的新型冠狀病毒（2019-nCoV，下稱武漢肺炎）疫情持續延燒，為防止疫情擴散，熊本縣當局宣布，5日起知名吉祥物熊本熊（くまモン） 將停止與觀眾直接接觸互動，這也是2013年以來，熊本熊首次執行相關禁令。<br />\n<br />\n綜合日媒報導，熊本市中央區的熊本熊廣場（くまモンスクエア）是觀光客喜愛前往的景點，除了可以近距離見到熊本熊，也可以和熊本熊握手、擁抱，但為了預防武漢肺炎疫情的擴散，當局宣布自5日起，將禁止遊客與熊本熊直接接觸。<br />\n<br />\n熊本熊廣場自上月25日起便積極宣導，要求工作人員並呼籲遊客戴上口罩，並向遊客提供中、英文版的宣傳手冊。據報導，該景點因可以近距離和熊本熊接觸，尤其受台灣、香港觀光客喜愛。<br />\n<br />\n在官方發布公告後，不少民眾表示可惜。一名台灣的旅客則對該措施表示理解，並稱自己喜歡熊本熊，因此也希望能守護牠。另一名來自大阪的遊客則表示，無法直接和熊本熊接觸令人沮喪，但也沒辦法，並表示自己還會再來。<br />\n<br />\n除熊本熊廣場外，該線的其他活動也將實行禁令，當局也表示，若疫情持續延燒，不排除將影響熊本熊3月的生日活動。據報導，目前東京迪士尼園區內的部分角色，也已停止與遊客接觸。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TzhQ4LX.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTzhQ4LX.gif&h=ca734984&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/amp/news/world/breakingnews/3059735\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Famp%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3059735&d=nNI0xXmu%2FnmsXsjxjv7MVZhvY2R4XAiH6OvuWOSnKsk%3D&h=4c219e48\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Famp%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3059735&h=72dc5813\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/amp/news/world/breakingnews/3059735</a>"},{"pid":"0abba455dcbb0caa1d425658b5abccdb6ddff0e8","tid":1872617,"uid":128271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T07:33:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />部長好正"},{"pid":"6ed25111583f3705c8f9ada10aae4419279e9291","tid":1872617,"uid":108236,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T07:34:18.000Z","msg":"月中去熊本<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />諗住去到扮熊本熊抽水<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11014892b5aab9b1fe06d68b8eb07d4bf673c92e","tid":1872617,"uid":60635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T07:40:00.000Z","msg":"無得同部長give me five<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea6578313d3b6b81fe4ecafbc08058c2296ae9b5","tid":1872617,"uid":63113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"11014892b5aab9b1fe06d68b8eb07d4bf673c92e","tid":1872617,"uid":60635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T07:40:00.000Z","msg":"無得同部長give me five<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T07:52:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xfCaksc.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxfCaksc.gif&h=23a61657&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6bc05efd1bcace1aa49d0314d2bd88d633b5147e","tid":1872617,"uid":294121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T07:58:05.000Z","msg":"講真如果日本人將熊本熊SET做肺炎死<br />\n唔會知唔會令到班日豚覺醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}